title Crear Notas SPA

browser->server: HTTP GET https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/spa
server-->browser: HTML-code
browser->server: HTTP GET https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/main.css
server-->browser: main.css
browser->server: HTTP GET https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/spa.js
server-->browser: spa.js

note over browser:
browser ejecuta el codigo js y solicita los datos 
end note

browser->server: HTTP GET https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/data.json
server-->browser: [{ content: "xxx", date: "xxxx-xx-xx" }, ...]

browser->server: HTTP GET https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/favicon.ico
server-->browser: favicon.ico

note over browser:
browser renderiza la informacion de las notas en pantalla
end note


note over browser:
New Note: el usuario carga el texto de una nota y presiona Save
end note


browser->server: HTTP POST https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/new_note_spa
browser->server: Solicita los datos de las notas asincronicamente

note over browser:
El browser solicita los nuevos datos al server de manera automatica
sin recargar todos los archivos y refresca la pantalla sin volver a cargar
end note
